@model AARP.Services.Emails.NotificationOfErrorEmail

@{
    var urlHangFireFaildJobs = Request.Url.Scheme + "/hangfire/failed";
}

To: @Model.To
From: internal@scopicsoftware.com
Subject: The RecruiterBox Tools was failed to proccess a background job after several retries

Hello,

Background job #@Model.HangfireContext.JobId (@Model.HangfireContext.Job.Method) was failed with an exception. 
Please click on the following link to get access to the job details: @urlHangFireFaildJobs

Exception message: @((Model.HangfireContext.NewState as Hangfire.States.FailedState).Exception.Message)

Please don’t reply to this email.